        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH7x2040-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:32:04.356+09:00">In Guìzhōu there are no donkeys.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:32:56.174+09:00">A busybody took one along in a boat and introduced it to the region.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:34:09.433+09:00">But when it arrived then there was nothing it could be used for,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:34:09.758+09:00">so he set the beast free at the foot of a mountain.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:34:25.118+09:00">A tiger caught sight of it:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:34:34.613+09:00">it was a huge creature,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:34:59.587+09:00">and the tiger thought it wa a ghost.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:35:43.136+09:00">Hiding among the trees he peered at it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:40:08.551+09:00">and by the bye he got closer to it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:40:42.204+09:00">but for all his thorough efforts he could not make head or tail of it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:40:56.92+09:00">The next day,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T07:18:02.485+09:00">                                    when the donkey gave one of his shrieks</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T07:18:03.712+09:00">                                    the tiger was greatly alarmed</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T07:18:00.971+09:00">                                    and sought refuge in the distance.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:43:56.039+09:00">He was under the impression that the beast was about to devour him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:44:36.752+09:00">He was terribly afraid.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:45:32.245+09:00">However, as he observed the beast over and over again</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:46:43.87+09:00">he discovered the it was a creature without any remarkable talents.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:47:52.396+09:00">As he familiarised himself with its voice</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:48:33.49+09:00">he moved out still closer, from in front and from the back,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:51:06.966+09:00">but to the very end he never plucked up the courage to grapple with the beast.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:51:37.305+09:00">He got a bit closer still,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T05:51:59.248+09:00">and he got increasingly familiar with it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:30:40.395+09:00">The donkey, unbearably enraged,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:30:47.031+09:00">kicked the man.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:31:21.809+09:00">The tiger, faced with this, was delighted.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:32:23.479+09:00">Assessing his opponent he said: "So this is all he is up to!"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:33:16.471+09:00">so he bounced over and with one great growl</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:34:05.387+09:00">he bit through his throat</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:35:29.215+09:00">finished off all the meat there was in him,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:40:38.378+09:00">噫！形之龐也，類有德。Ah, great size of body gives the impression on has virtue,聲之宏也，類有能。a resounding voice gives the impression one has talent向不出其技，虎雖猛，疑畏卒不敢取。Before, he had not displayed his (limited) skills, and the tiger, fierce as he was, was diffident  and awe-struck and did not have the courage to take the beast.今若是焉，悲夫！But now the poor beast is in this state: How sad!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2040_CHANT_030-14a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-23T06:40:30.223+09:00">and went his way.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
